<section class="section blog-section" id="blog">
  <div class="blog-content">
    <h2 class="blog-title reveal">Thoughts & Stories</h2>
    <p class="blog-intro reveal">
      Beyond the code, there are stories worth telling. From firefighting lessons 
      that apply to debugging, to the human side of building technology.
    </p>
    
    <div class="blog-preview reveal">
      <div class="coming-soon">Coming Soon</div>
      <h3>What I'll be writing about</h3>
      <p>
        Real stories from the intersection of emergency response and software engineering. 
        Lessons learned from scaling systems, leading teams, and building products 
        that actually matter to people.
      </p>
      
      <div class="blog-topics">
        <span class="blog-topic">Serverless Architecture</span>
        <span class="blog-topic">Leadership Lessons</span>
        <span class="blog-topic">From Firefighter to CTO</span>
        <span class="blog-topic">Building for Impact</span>
        <span class="blog-topic">International Perspectives</span>
      </div>
      
      <a href="/blog" class="blog-cta">
        <span>Follow the journey</span>
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M7 17l9.2-9.2M17 17V7H7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Blog section */
  .blog-section {
    background: rgba(0, 78, 137, 0.03);
  }

  .blog-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .blog-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .blog-intro {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .blog-preview {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .blog-preview::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.05),
      transparent
    );
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    transition: all 0.6s ease;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .blog-preview:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
    animation: shine 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  .blog-preview:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
  }

  .coming-soon {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #ff6b35;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .blog-preview h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .blog-preview p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .blog-topics {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .blog-topic {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.15);
    border-radius: 25px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #ff6b35;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
  }

  .blog-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid #ff6b35;
    color: #ff6b35;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .blog-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    background: #ff6b35;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: all 0.6s ease;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .blog-cta:hover::before {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
  }

  .blog-cta:hover {
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @keyframes shine {
    0% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateX(-100%); }
    100% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateX(100%); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-topics {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
    .blog-preview {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>